title: Canada : Gross Domestic Product ( GDP ) by industry December 2019
yAxis: GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars
summary: This is a bar chart representing Industry in the x axis and GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars in the y axis.
The GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars is appeared to be the highest at Industry Real estate and rental and leasing and lowest at Industry Management of companies and enterprises.
There is a difference of 244991.0 between the maximum Industry Real estate and rental and leasing and minimum Industry Management of companies and enterprises.

max_summary: This is a bar chart. It shows GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars for 20 number of Industrys.
The GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars is appeared to be the highest at Industry Real estate and rental and leasing and lowest at Industry Management of companies and enterprises.
There is a difference of 244991.0 between the maximum Industry Real estate and rental and leasing and minimum Industry Management of companies and enterprises.

GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars at Industry Real estate and rental and leasing is 254294.0 , second place is Manufacturing at 199234.0, and thirdly is Mining quarrying and oil and gas extraction at 145909.0.
The Industry Real estate and rental and leasing tends to be 2.57 percent higher than average.
The GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars is 1981842.0 if we add up values of all Industrys.
